  torque-2.2.1-r2.ebuild, -torque-2.3.0.ebuild, torque-2.3.0-r1.ebuild:
  Remove blocker on x11-misc/qterm (Bug #176533). Add blocker on
  games-util/qstat (Bug #207059).  Drop old version.

